Class ReportDAO.ZReportData

java.lang.Object
database.ReportDAO.ZReportData
Enclosing class:
ReportDAO
public static class ReportDAO.ZReportData extends Object
Represents structured data for the end-of-day Z-Report summary. Includes transaction counts, revenue totals, and employee signatures.
